Get standardized WAIS-R Digit Symbol score

standardized_cog_digsym.Rd

Get standardized WAIS-R Digit Symbol score

Usage

standardized_cog_digsym(cog_digsym, digsym_age_groups)

Arguments

cog_digsym

Raw score

digsym_age_groups

age group; a vector of same length as cog_digsym with entries as one of the following

  • 'AAAA' for ages 45-54

  • 'BBBB' for ages 55-64

  • 'CCCC' for ages 65-69

  • 'DDDD' for ages 70-74

  • 'EEEE' for ages 75-79

  • 'FFFF' for ages 80+

Value

A numeric vector of same length as cog_digsym with the standardized scores.

Examples

standardized_cog_digsym(24, 'DDDD')
#> [1] 8
